## Naming Convention

### Required Format

```
{audit_type}_audit_{YYYY-MM-DD}.md
```

**Components:**
- `{audit_type}` - Type of audit in `snake_case`
- `_audit_` - Literal string (required)
- `{YYYY-MM-DD}` - Date of audit

### Audit Type Examples

| Audit Type | Filename |
|------------|----------|
| Project Structure | `project_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Security | `security_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Documentation | `documentation_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Code Quality | `code_quality_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Dependencies | `dependency_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Database | `database_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Performance | `performance_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Accessibility | `accessibility_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| API | `api_audit_2025-12-09.md` |
| Custom | `{description}_audit_2025-12-09.md` |

### Multiple Audits Same Day

If running multiple audits of the same type on the same day, append a sequence number:
```
security_audit_2025-12-09_01.md
security_audit_2025-12-09_02.md
```

